00:14:27.040 --> 00:14:28.340
OK.

00:14:28.340 --> 00:14:29.640
&gt;&gt; Joe Palca: Yeah.

00:14:29.640 --> 00:14:30.940
&gt;&gt; James Gleick: That
looked about 50/50.

00:14:30.940 --> 00:14:32.240
&gt;&gt; Joe Palca: Yeah.

00:14:32.240 --> 00:14:33.540
&gt;&gt; James Gleick: Now,
I've heard it theorized,

00:14:33.540 --> 00:14:34.970
I don't endorse this theory that--

00:14:34.970 --> 00:14:38.490
and I don't have a new
