00:14:44.050 --> 00:14:46.050
I don't know.

00:14:46.050 --> 00:14:49.420
And you're suggesting maybe
that the literary folk are

00:14:49.420 --> 00:14:51.000
more past-oriented?

00:14:51.000 --> 00:14:52.300
&gt;&gt; Joe Palca: Well, I mean,

00:14:52.300 --> 00:14:53.980
