00:20:01.210 --> 00:20:03.410
[ Laughter ]

00:20:03.410 --> 00:20:04.710
But it's also--

00:20:04.710 --> 00:20:06.750 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Joe Palca: I hope you sharpen
