00:21:23.070 --> 00:21:26.560 position:56%
So, there isn't as-- I'm not
willing to give a definitive answer,

00:21:26.560 --> 00:21:30.100
I'm willing to say,
any kid who is arguing

00:21:30.100 --> 00:21:35.490
about it is thinking
along productive lines.

00:21:35.490 --> 00:21:36.790
&gt;&gt; Joe Palca: Yeah.

00:21:36.790 --> 00:21:41.600
Yeah. What is-- The other thing
