00:22:03.550 --> 00:22:05.490
like the book "Flatland," where--

00:22:05.490 --> 00:22:06.790
&gt;&gt; James Gleick: Yeah.

00:22:06.790 --> 00:22:08.090
&gt;&gt; Joe Palca: -- the people
