00:23:31.080 --> 00:23:32.380
And he says, "No.

00:23:32.380 --> 00:23:35.440
Think about it, isn't
duration also a dimension?"

00:23:35.440 --> 00:23:38.220
And they go on like that.

00:23:38.220 --> 00:23:47.010
And it's 1895, it's 10
years later that Einstein

00:23:47.010 --> 00:23:53.730
