in which time is just

00:24:09.120 --> 00:24:11.370
like the other three dimensions.

00:24:11.370 --> 00:24:15.760
Mathematically, it's treated
the same way and that means

00:24:15.760 --> 00:24:18.020
that mathematically speaking,
there's no difference

00:24:18.020 --> 00:24:20.610
in the equations between
the past and the future.

00:24:20.610 --> 00:24:25.210
And this is, you know,
