trying to wrap their minds

00:25:24.480 --> 00:25:26.790
around the idea of
a third dimension.

00:25:26.790 --> 00:25:29.970
And we, as three-dimensional
creatures have the advantage

00:25:29.970 --> 00:25:31.270
