00:26:41.340 --> 00:26:44.860
like H.G. Wells were letting
their thinking explode,

00:26:44.860 --> 00:26:47.800
I think for the same reasons.

00:26:47.800 --> 00:26:51.250 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Joe Palca: So, I-- my background,

