00:27:01.750 --> 00:27:04.240
And I wonder if you talk
a little bit about that.

00:27:04.240 --> 00:27:10.220
And is time the same for you and
me and people on the other side

00:27:10.220 --> 00:27:14.540
of the universe or is it mutable?

00:27:15.720 --> 00:27:18.010
&gt;&gt; James Gleick: You
