that it's the same
everywhere in the universe.

00:28:13.730 --> 00:28:18.050
And let's just treat it that
way, as absolute and universal.

00:28:18.050 --> 00:28:23.860
And fine, that worked really great
as everybody knows until Einstein.

00:28:23.860 --> 00:28:30.480
And Einstein changed
that and discovered

00:28:30.480 --> 00:28:33.510
that there are some slippage,

00:28:33.510 --> 00:28:41.780
and maybe not as much
slippage as we tend to think.

00:28:41.780 --> 00:28:46.790 position:56%
I tend to feel-- and you don't have
to consider me an authority on this,

00:28:46.790 --> 00:28:48.360
this could be a matter
of prejudice--

00:28:48.360 --> 00:28:53.740
I tend to feel that Einstein
was himself very much supporting

00:28:53.740 --> 00:28:58.470
Newton's, the main distinction
Newton was making which was

00:28:58.470 --> 00:29:03.500
